### Authentication API Tests
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api

### Login as Superadmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "superadmin@test.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Login as Admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@test.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Login as Dean
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "dean@test.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Login as Faculty
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "faculty@test.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Login as Organization
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "org@test.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Get Profile (Replace YOUR_TOKEN with actual token from login response)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

###

### Test Superadmin Dashboard (Replace YOUR_TOKEN)
GET {{baseUrl}}/superadmin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

###

### Test Admin Dashboard (Replace YOUR_TOKEN)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

###

### Test Dean Dashboard (Replace YOUR_TOKEN)
GET {{baseUrl}}/dean/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

###

### Test Faculty Dashboard (Replace YOUR_TOKEN)
GET {{baseUrl}}/faculty/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

###

### Test Organization Dashboard (Replace YOUR_TOKEN)
GET {{baseUrl}}/organization/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

###

### Register New User (Example)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newuser@test.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "admin"
}

###

### Create Superadmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/create-superadmin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "superadmin@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePassword123!"
}

###

### Create Admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/create-admin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "first_name": "John",
  "middle_name": "M",
  "last_name": "Doe",
  "contact_number": "09123456789"
}

